verbose_text: In the allele model, we discovered that rs791588 (IL2RA) and rs2281089 (IL2RB) significantly decreased the risk of RA in females (rs791588 : OR = 0.49, 95% CI = 0.30-0.82, p = 0.006) and people aged under 54 (rs2281089 : OR = 0.37, 95% CI = 0.21-0.68, p = 0.001 and OR = 0.72, 95% CI = 0.56-0.93, p = 0.011).
evidence: rs2281089 (IL2RB) significantly decreased the risk of RA
